metadata.name: QUEEN
metadata.description:
The beautiful representation of Q U E E N is illustrated in black and white to reflect the value of nature and human beings. The existence of nudity should be embraced in a way to celebrate the evolution of human beings! QUEEN is beautiful and everyone is beautiful! 

Art by Simron Raj
Edition : 1/1 
year : 2022
